    bounds_list = list(bounds)

    def move_to(x, y):

        x = max(x_min, min(x, x_max))
        y = max(y_min, min(y, y_max))
        position[0] = x
        position[1] = y

        x = max(x_min, min(x, x_max))
        y = max(y_min, min(y, y_max))
        position[0] = x
        position[1] = y
    return (set_bounds, move_to, draw_line)
